Alien-Libssh2
=============

Alien::Libssh2 is a helper module for downloading, configuring,
building and installing libssh2 in order to be used by other Perl
modules and specifically by Net::SSH2.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
        ./Build installdeps
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT

For support go to the GitHub repository:

https://github.com/salva/p5-Alien-Libssh2

